4/140424screenshot.png\" alt=\"140424screenshot\" width=\"970\" height=\"263\" /></a>\r\n<h3>\'Magic guessing\' for new trackings</h3>\r\nWe call it “the magic guessing” - the add/edit times dialog now offers a list of computed work items for that particular day, based on what was assigned to you, in process and in frequent use - the first item has a good chance to be the one to book your times on.\r\n<h3>Access your queries for selecting items in new trackings</h3>\r\nThe next help for the add/edit times dialog - a selector that presents you items to choose from based on the available queries in Team Foundation Server - personal and shared.\r\n<h3>Budgets reloaded</h3>\r\nThe view “Budgets” was redesigned, it consists now of a list on the left side and a detail view on the right. The detail view informs in addition about what is counted in the total sum, included and excluded iterations and items.\r\n<h3>Who doesn\'t like speed?</h3>\r\nWe again managed to eliminate some speed bottle necks, page loading time was greatly reduced.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '2.4 Is Here With Seven Big News!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '740-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-24 17:03:17', '2014-04-24 17:03:17', '', '740', 'http://www.tfs-timetracker.com/740-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
