INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1267', '1', '2015-09-11 09:25:17', '2015-09-11 09:25:17', '<h1>Additional service release for Team Foundation Server 2015</h1>\r\nWednesday evening we have released the 2.6.6 which fixes a bug that rarely affects some systems with Team Foundation Server 2015.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nIn this case the TFS Timetracker Client for Windows was not able to connect to the server and connection errors occured.\r\n\r\nThe release of TFS Timetracker 2.6.6 resolves that issue.\r\n\r\nPlease take our apologies that it was needed to adjust the release for Team Foundation Server 2015 one more time in such a short timeframe. There were quite a lot changes from Team Foundation Server RC1 to its final release (RTM), which made an unusual amount of adjustments necessary. While we are doing our best to test all possible scenarios that might happen, some gaps remain. The two last releases were necessary upon reports from users to our support. Thank you guys for reporting this and helping us to fix it that quickly!', 'TFS Timetracker 2.6.6', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1264-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 09:25:17', '2015-09-11 09:25:17', '', '1264', 'http://blog.tfs-timetracker.com/1264-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
